Package: remart
Title: Reimplementation of the 'biomaRt' Package Using Modern Ensembl APIs
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Hugo", "Gruson", , "hugo.gruson@embl.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package aims to offer a drop-in replacement to biomaRt
    using the same interface but the more modern and better maintained
    APIs provided by Ensembl.
